    <div xlink:href="41467_2018_4173_Article_Equ8.gif" position="anchor" class="graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
   </div>
  </div>where the terms on the right-hand side each represent an individual warming contribution and together sum to the total surface warming Δ
  <span class="italic">T</span>
  <sub>s</sub> (with small residual ignored here); 
  <div id="IEq5" class="inline-formula">
   <div class="alternatives">
    <span id="M25" class="tex-math">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$\lambda _0^\prime = \lambda _0 - \overline {\lambda _0}$$\end{document}</span>
